fix(hero): shorten mobile scroll-pin from 1800px to 700px

Users on mobile had to swipe ~3 times to get past the pinned
CinematicHero timeline. Reducing the ScrollTrigger end from +=1800
to +=700 means one swipe (~1 viewport height) completes the
animation and unpins the hero.

Also includes improved STRIPE_FAIL error logging in
/api/stripe/checkout (from the env-var corruption debugging).
